#: ../../E/examining-the-entrails.rst:9
msgid ""
"The process of :ref:`grovel`\\ling through a :ref:`core-dump` or hex image "
"in an attempt to discover the bug that brought a program or system down. The"
" reference is to divination from the entrails of a sacrificed animal. "
"Compare :ref:`runes`\\, :ref:`incantation`\\, :ref:`black-art`\\."
msgstr ""
"プログラムやシステムをダウンさせたバグを発見しようと、\\ :ref:`core-dump`\\ や16進イメージの中を\\ "
":ref:`grovel`\\ する過程。この言い回しは、生贄の動物の内臓による占いを指している。\\ :ref:`runes`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`incantation`\\ 、\\ :ref:`black-art`\\ と比較せよ。"
